snippet.title: Octave Gameplay demo
snippet.description:
Octave is a point-and-click horror adventure with action elements. 

The game is about a guy who happened at the wrong time in the wrong place. 
Someone or something had saved his life in the woods, but the more he sneaks into the forest, 
the more he realize that salvation can turn into a nightmare and the struggle for the life has just begun.
